title: Samsung Galaxy Active Neo Rugged Smartphone Launches in Japan - newsR
text: If you missed seeing Samsung unveil a new smartphone, today the wait has come to an end, as the Korean tech giant has just launched a new terminal in Japan. The model arrives in the wild as the Galaxy Active Neo, and as the naming scheme suggests, it’s a rugged but budget-friendly device. Since we said budget, you shouldn’t be expecting the device to feature stellar specs, but cover just the bear minimum you need to be getting through the day. The phone comes with a TFT LCD... »
